<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4577190>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Comparison of shell profile, breathing tube, and peristome of Opisthoporus spp. in Vietnam. A, D, G, Opisthoporus beddomei (ZMHU/5), with oblique breathing tube and double peristome; B, E, H, Opisthoporus lubricus (ZMHU/4), with forward pointing breathing tube and double peristome; C, F, I, Opisthoporus thuathienhuensis, new species (holotype VNMN_IZ 000.000.176), with inverted U-shaped breathing tube and single peristome. Photographs by D.S. Do and T.S. Nguyen." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4577190/files/figure.png" .

